1 FOR BICYCLING, HIKING, EQUESTRIAN USE, OR OTHER ACTIVE OR PASSIVE
2 RECREATIONAL USE.
3 (4) THE DEPARTMENT SHALL:
4 (I) MAP AREAS OF THE STATE TO WHICH A PERMIT MAY APPLY
5 UNDER THIS SUBSECTION; AND
6 (II) MAKE THE MAPS READILY AVAILABLE TO THE PUBLIC.
