20 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That, on or before December 1,
21 2029, the Department of Natural Resources shall:
22 (1) report to the General Assembly, in accordance with § 2–1257 of the
23 State Government Article, on the effectiveness of this Act on deer management and
24 balancing stakeholder interests; and
25 (2) include in the report input from all relevant stakeholders.
26 SECTION 4. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act may not be construed
27 to authorize the Department of Natural Resources to allow Sunday hunting in Baltimore
28 County, Howard County, or Prince George’s County:
29 (1) (i) except as provided in Section 10–410(a)(9) through (11) of the
30 Natural Resources Article, as enacted by Section 1 of this Act; and

