4 Natural Resources Article, as enacted by Section 2 of this Act; and
5 (ii) subject to Section 10–410(a)(2) of the Natural Resources Article,
6 as enacted by Section 2 of this Act.
7 SECTION 5. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That Section 2 of this Act shall take
8 effect July 1, 2027. It shall remain effective for a period of 3 years and, at the end of June
9 30, 2030, Section 2 of this Act, with no further action required by the General Assembly,
10 shall be abrogated and of no further force and effect.
11 SECTION 5. 6. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That, except as provided in
